{
  "stem": "27150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That means for this trip, I was wearing two suits and a fur coat, you see.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That [INAUDIBLE] this was a sort of a necessity because [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the fur coats and the things-- and lucky we had it because we took it down to them, the [INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "SS, ?] you see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if they would arrest us, they would have to take all the stuff to the headquarters.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Apparently, they took it for themselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Go away Jew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you see, so-- so we were free, but they had all our addresses and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went to-- to sleep to my parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, all the time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- and-- and in the meantime, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rom ?] and Robin came back and told us that-- that-- that had-- he had to clean a lavatory without a brush.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's no business to stay with the Germans, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] so, you see, the industry, there were a lot of salesmen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the smuggling industry east-- well, east and westwards-- was blooming, you see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were hundreds of smugglers, you see, and friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, I'll take you over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We took-- that makes a smaller group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went to-- in another goods truck, covered, you see, with some hay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We went towards [NON-ENGLISH], which was a border town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A truck a goods truck, which on top carried merchandise, and we were sort of hidden.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is my wife, myself, my brother, my sister-in-law, and a couple of friends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Parents said, you young people, you go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the message was that in Russia is-- there's no anti-semitism, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what do they want from old people?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We will survive or not they said.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
